data.text:
-> TNPSC Group 2 Notification has been released. A total of 2327 Vacancies have been announced for the post of Combined Civil Services Examination - II (Group II and IIA Services).

-> Candidates can apply for the posts from 20th June 2024 to 19th July 2024.

-> The Date of the Preliminary Examination is 14th September 2024. The Mains date will be announced later.

-> The Application Correction Window will open for three days from 24.07.2024 to 26.07.2024

-> It has post like Assistant Section Officer, Revenue Assistant, Assistant, etc.
